  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2007-12-12",
    "date": "2008-04-10T16:49:48Z",
    "text": "Toy Origin for Toddler Safety Act - Amends the Consumer Product Safety Act to require every manufacturer of a consumer product to post on its website (if any) the location of the facility where the product was manufactured or assembled. Requires the manufacturer, if similar products are manufactured or assembled at multiple facilities, to make such information available by serial number or other identifier."
